rows.label: qst200709_msg0001
rows.name:
This area is off-limits to
unauthorized personnel. I'm
sorry, but please leave.

rows.label: qst200709_msg0002
rows.name:
Can't you do something
about that-mau? I'll pay
up to 3000G in bribes-mau.

rows.label: qst200709_msg0003
rows.name:
I absolutely have to get to
His Majesty the Emperor-mau!

rows.label: qst200709_msg0004
rows.name:
What a persistent fellow. Do
you think I'd let someone who
brazenly offers bribes pass?!

rows.label: qst200709_msg0006
rows.name:
Or would you rather be
arrested and thrown in jail?!
